## Appendix A: Derivation of I_ext Formula

Starting from two coherent oscillators with amplitudes A₁ and A₂ and phase difference θ:

$$A_{total} = A_1e^{i\phi_1} + A_2e^{i\phi_2}$$

$$|A_{total}|^2 = A_1^2 + A_2^2 + 2A_1A_2\cos(\phi_2 - \phi_1)$$

Identifying A₁ = C₁, A₂ = C₂, and θ = φ₂ - φ₁:

$$I_{ext}^2 = C_1^2 + C_2^2 + 2C_1C_2\cos(θ)$$

$$I_{ext} = \sqrt{C_1^2 + C_2^2 + 2C_1C_2\cos(θ)}$$

